{"tid":834101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【三等殖民】支那客大篋來港無阻   港客要用「紅白藍」","createTime":"2018-09-24T03:35:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T13:12:47.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"41fc3a10b2c08113b3a95a9cac934b3ff1c43d13","tid":834101,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T03:35:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180924/s00001/1537728543889\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180924%2Fs00001%2F1537728543889&d=PDhiVWoQ4brW0VOu49aGqwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=0256c6d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180924%2Fs00001%2F1537728543889&h=e2e9d56b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180924/s00001/1537728543889</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20180924/s00006/4d9bef9b08ae469767e6bc21face650b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20180924%2Fs00006%2F4d9bef9b08ae469767e6bc21face650b.jpg&h=562bfbdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】由高鐵香港段出發的乘客，可帶上列車行李的長闊高相加不可超過130厘米，卻出現行李箱要求「一鐵兩制」。有港客攜帶過大行李，最終需將篋內私人物品轉放到紅白藍袋帶走，對此深感不滿；有內地乘客稱內地安檢並無提及有關限制，順利從內地帶了超大行李乘車來港，但擔心返程時不准帶上車。<br />\n<br />\n「為何上到飛機上不到高鐵？」<br />\n<br />\n香港乘客羅先生攜帶了兩個行李篋，站內職員量度尺寸，其中一件的高度超出限制，較另一件高出約兩吋。職員拒絕讓他帶該行李篋，建議他改用港鐵免費提供的紅白藍袋，並將該行李篋存放站內，待他返港後取回。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵通車前有宣傳行李尺碼要求，傳媒亦有報道，但羅先生稱不知有行李限制，對此深感不滿，「有什麼理由（行李）上到飛機，但上不到高鐵？」他說平常人旅行也不會用紅白藍袋，認為限制不合理。<br />\n<br />\n記者帶同32吋行李篋入閘，也被職員指尺寸超標，要求記者寄存行李箱，但箱內物品要自行帶走。港鐵提供紅白藍袋，職員要求乘客填寫表格，留下姓名及聯絡電話等資料，乘客需在1個月內憑底單到站取回。但記者上車後，發現同一班車有不少人順利帶同大件行李上車，行李箱尺寸與記者的相若。<br />\n<br />\n而從上海乘高鐵來港的彭小姐攜帶了一個超大行李篋，她說在上海過安檢時無人告知她有關行李限制，她有購買回程票，擔心屆時攜帶該件行李離境時會被拒絕。"},{"pid":"a24fed7756b81931f317369f0f1fff822192a19c","tid":834101,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T09:58:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9b9ba1a908b8a33b6fc9bcc25de8d71b5e326fa","tid":834101,"uid":65056,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T10:05:43.000Z","msg":"問題既重點係係邊到上車，大陸上就冇問題，香港上港鐵會渣正黎做<br />\n<br />\n完全體現兩地人質素既分別"},{"pid":"eee4c501b6b85c75c87857bc58ec064afd190a23","tid":834101,"uid":99700,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T10:06:34.000Z","msg":"狗先搭高鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你唔認自己係狗人地都當你狗咁撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa71c7315bd91a4766ccd95db85d26bd3bf9bbf","tid":834101,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T12:11:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c9c2b92f5e7298b0dc8f590bddc1d7dadd410ee","tid":834101,"uid":26770,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f9b9ba1a908b8a33b6fc9bcc25de8d71b5e326fa","tid":834101,"uid":65056,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T10:05:43.000Z","msg":"問題既重點係係邊到上車，大陸上就冇問題，香港上港鐵會渣正黎做<br />\n<br />\n完全體現兩地人質素既分別"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T12:20:26.000Z","msg":"你都on99<br />\n<br />\n香港人report大陸客食野,mtr dog放生大陸人,仲恐嚇投訴人你再投訴就出告票罰你錢"},{"pid":"34d6971d6bb161751d3894a3484426c1dbb4aee3","tid":834101,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T12:28:32.000Z","msg":"特權階級嘛, 色目人"},{"pid":"f1ed691817859e3a19262e4b60710d31f0115854","tid":834101,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T12:29:40.000Z","msg":"一早話高鐵起黎為支那人服務<br />\n港豬而家信未？"},{"pid":"2b74ea98d3b7b11ffde7d4b58eb41485833b9857","tid":834101,"uid":25900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1ed691817859e3a19262e4b60710d31f0115854","tid":834101,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T12:29:40.000Z","msg":"一早話高鐵起黎為支那人服務<br />\n港豬而家信未？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T12:30:53.000Z","msg":"班垃圾一日未比針吉一日都唔會痛"},{"pid":"cfdf9c692460c32ef3c6255331a2f87c61c66676","tid":834101,"uid":106247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T12:36:24.000Z","msg":"由班港豬搭飽佢<br />\n真係要返大陸都搭飛機好過鳩鐵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9f3cba5de625eb051edab4bbccd2bd64bbb095","tid":834101,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T12:39:26.000Z","msg":"一定要話返俾羅先生知，要佢眼火爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4de4dccd21fc38d298fcb6d55a06394c312940d","tid":834101,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b74ea98d3b7b11ffde7d4b58eb41485833b9857","tid":834101,"uid":25900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1ed691817859e3a19262e4b60710d31f0115854","tid":834101,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T12:29:40.000Z","msg":"一早話高鐵起黎為支那人服務<br />\n港豬而家信未？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T12:30:53.000Z","msg":"班垃圾一日未比針吉一日都唔會痛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T13:12:47.000Z","msg":"食花生睇戲好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}